--------------------------------------------------
VISUAL STYLE DIRECTION
--------------------------------------------------

Create a UNIQUE VISUAL EXPERIENCE using these principles:

1. LAYERED DEPTH
- Use layered surfaces, translucent panels, controlled glass effects
- Rich depth hierarchy between background / panel / active surface / floating UI
- Create a premium sense of spatial separation

2. EDITORIAL SPACING
- Use bold whitespace intentionally
- Give every section room to breathe
- Make the layout feel designed, not packed

3. STRONG TYPOGRAPHY SYSTEM
- Typography must feel elite and product-grade
- Use a premium font pairing
- Example direction:
  - Headings: Inter Tight / Satoshi / Plus Jakarta Sans / Geist / Manrope
  - Body: Inter / Manrope / SF-like clean system pairing
  - Mono/code: JetBrains Mono / Geist Mono
- Typography should create hierarchy instantly
- Avoid default “all text looks same” problem

4. RICH VISUAL TEXTURE
- Add subtle mesh gradients / ambient lighting / premium surface textures
- Use controlled highlights, not loud gamer effects
- Use restrained sophistication

5. PREMIUM COLOR SYSTEM
- Create a branded, memorable palette
- Avoid overused AI purple-blue gradient cliché
- Introduce a refined, original accent system
- Use dark mode that feels luxurious, not dull
- Optional direction:
  - graphite / obsidian / deep navy base
  - champagne / electric cyan / muted emerald / aurora accents
- Ensure every accent has a purpose

6. MICRO-INTERACTIONS
- Every hover, click, expand, focus, tab switch, and load should feel alive
- Add subtle but premium motion
- Motion should communicate intelligence and polish
- Avoid gimmicks

7. VISUAL RHYTHM
- Different component densities across the page
- Some zones should feel calm and minimal
- Some zones should feel powerful and data-rich
- Avoid one-density UI everywhere

